<p>John and Dave take you through managing your media perfectly for your new &ndash; and old &ndash; Apple TV, including using a NAS to store it all if you like. Then it&#39;s some tips about speeding up Time Machine, speeding up App Store downloads, converting movies and sound issues. Pepper in some additional questions and listener Cool Stuff Found and you&#39;ve got a full show!</p>
